{"type": "article", "id": 21441, "title": "最佳钢琴品牌之一施坦威，在日本开了相当优雅的旗舰店", "description": "这些垂直的琴弦让这个房间充满了平静和紧张。", "date": "2016-01-28T15:12:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3000, "name": "店铺设计"}, {"id": 6719, "name": "钢琴"}, {"id": 2862, "name": "旗舰店"}, {"id": 7137, "name": "东京"}, {"id": 19412, "name": "SALT"}, {"id": 22842, "name": "steinway&sons"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 239, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702141541GcOsbMN2jArUfSXT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>美国钢琴品牌 steinway&amp;sons（施坦威）在日本东京开了一家亚洲旗舰店。这家成立于 1853 年的<span>品牌</span>源于一对<span>移民纽约</span>的德国父子，目前是业内公认为最好也是最贵的一家。他们邀请日本的建筑事务所 Salt 做室内设计，要体现出它的历史、手工艺和理念。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>进入商店前需要经过一个接待室，类似于欧洲的庄园。一侧墙面涂上黑漆，展示了施坦威 125 项设计专利，据说涂黑漆来保护器物的方式也是钢琴黑色涂层的起源。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>“人”字形的斜纹木地板使用了 5 种木材，来自制作钢琴所需的 5 种材料，榉木、花梨木、胡桃木、枫木和红木。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141533AJnudq9Mx10r7zHw.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141534QBpvH2IT5jc1f7mk.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>另一侧墙面放置了和施坦威有关的文献，介绍了品牌的历史。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141535Utd21INQPeBaGoxc.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150949hSTJ2dtjb9ZcDgea.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>墙的后面有两间调音室，分别用了花梨木和枫木，只放了一架三角钢琴。木质墙面像肋骨一样有着凹凸的层次，墙面有着凹进去纹路，类似于三角形的琴盖。另一个房间的凹凸感更有规则，近似于琴键，木片方正而有节奏。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141535kyuzxvfJ2dIpQXne.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141536aQzPGV3WyoCruKb5.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141536ry8U1Pi5mhIV4SX0.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>展示间也用浅色的木材包裹，墙面的木条是黑键和白键的关系，错落起伏，让房间充满了音乐感。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141537pVmSgvXkFsQny8qo.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141537b6EkaqpHz5O9yZVf.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>靠近玻璃窗的地方安置了 12,000 根不锈钢丝，以呼应钢琴琴弦。一架钢琴的琴弦可以承受 20 吨的张力，但这种张力一般是看不见的，设计者称这些垂直的<span>钢丝</span>让这个房间充满了平静和紧张，“当人们走到跟前，似乎能感受到颤抖的屏幕和其中蕴含的音乐。”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141538omBwsaicdtHDZQOT.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141538Jd63B4wLQ5bgXoiD.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141539iyvLn6hz5Tu9a0XV.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702141540MaURzxqiO1EhyX3B.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1404\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/01/26/salt-steinway-son-tokyo-showroom-piano-components/\" target=\"_blank\">dezeen</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}